{"word":"φυλία","slug":"φυλία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n112565\" key=\"fuli/a\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">φῠλία</orth>, poet. <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">φῡλετ-ίη</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, a tree mentioned with the olive in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:5:477\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.477</biblScope> </bibl> (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">δοιοὺς . . θάμνους, ἐξ ὁμόθεν πεφυῶτας—ὁ μὲν φυλίης, ὁ δ᾽ ἐλαίης</etym>), apptly. (cf. Sch.ad loc., <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hsch.\">Hsch.</a></author> </bibl>) a kind of <sense id=\"n112565.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">wild olive,</tr_> but distd. fr. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κότινος</foreign> and said to be Troezenian by <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0525.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:32:10\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Paus.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.32.10</biblScope> </bibl> (written <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">φυλλία</foreign>), cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0638.tlg007:43\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Philostr.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Gym.\">Gym.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">43</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2045.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:474\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Nonn.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.474</biblScope> </bibl>; wrongly identified by <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0708.tlg001:p.135V\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Ammon.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Diff.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">p.135V.</biblScope> </bibl> with <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σχῖνος.</foreign> </sense> </entryFree>"}]}